    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bowls of varying form but usually lidded, intended primarily for holding and serving sugar; made as an individual piece, to match a creamer, or as part of a tea or coffee service.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
